{"pageProps":{"post":{"attributes":{},"html":"<h1 id=\"update-the-router\">Update the router</h1>\n<p>In the <code>services/Router.js</code> replace the <code>go</code> function</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-js\"> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">go</span>: <span class=\"hljs-function\">(<span class=\"hljs-params\">route, addToHistory=<span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span></span>) =&gt;</span> {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (addToHistory) {\n        history.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">pushState</span>({ route }, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span>, route);\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> pageElement = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">switch</span> (route) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/&quot;</span>:\n            pageElement = <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">document</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">createElement</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;menu-page&quot;</span>);\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>;\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/order&quot;</span>:\n            pageElement = <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">document</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">createElement</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;order-page&quot;</span>);\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>;\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">default</span>:\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (route.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">startsWith</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/product-&quot;</span>)) {                \n                pageElement = <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">document</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">createElement</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;details-page&quot;</span>);\n                pageElement.<span class=\"hljs-property\">dataset</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">productId</span> = route.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">substring</span>(route.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">lastIndexOf</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;-&quot;</span>)+<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>);\n            }\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>;   \n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (pageElement) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">document</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">querySelector</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;main&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">innerHTML</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&quot;</span>;\n        <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">document</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">querySelector</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;main&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">appendChild</span>(pageElement);\n    }\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">scrollX</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Check DevTools and Inspect the current HTML.</p>\n","slug":"update-the-router copy","title":"Update the Router Copy","section":"Web Components","icon":"puzzle-piece","filePath":"/Users/firt/Library/Mobile Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/Trainings/FEM/YDNTL/vanilla/lessons/04-web-components/B-update-the-router copy.md","nextSlug":"/vanilla/lessons/web-components/use-the-templates","prevSlug":"/vanilla/lessons/web-components/create-the-custom-elements"}},"__N_SSG":true}